<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="zh-TW">

<head>

    <meta charset="UTF-8">

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>許毓庭的個人網站</title>

    <style>

        :root {

            --primary-color: #2c3e50;

            --accent-color: #3498db;

            --bg-color: #f4f7f6;

            --text-color: #333;

        }



        body {

            font-family: "Microsoft JhengHei", Arial, sans-serif;

            background-color: var(--bg-color);

            color: var(--text-color);

            line-height: 1.6;

            margin: 0;

            display: flex;

            justify-content: center;

            align-items: center;

            min-height: 100vh;

        }



        .card {

            background: white;

            width: 90%;

            max-width: 500px;

            padding: 40px;

            border-radius: 15px;

            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);

            text-align: center;

        }



        .profile-header {

            margin-bottom: 30px;

        }



        h1 {

            color: var(--primary-color);

            margin: 10px 0;

            letter-spacing: 2px;

        }



        .tag {

            background: var(--accent-color);

            color: white;

            padding: 5px 15px;

            border-radius: 20px;

            font-size: 0.9em;

        }



        .info-section {

            text-align: left;

            margin-top: 30px;

            border-top: 1px solid #eee;

            padding-top: 20px;

        }



        .info-item {

            margin-bottom: 12px;

            display: flex;

            align-items: center;

        }



        .info-label {

            font-weight: bold;

            width: 80px;

            color: var(--accent-color);

        }



        .goal-box {

            background: #eef7fd;

            padding: 15px;

            border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-color);

            margin-top: 20px;

            font-style: italic;

            border-radius: 4px;

        }



        footer {

            margin-top: 30px;

            font-size: 0.8em;

            color: #888;

        }

    </style>

</head>

<body>



    <div class="card">

        <div class="profile-header">

            <span class="tag">Hello World!</span>

            <h1>許毓庭</h1>

            <p>18 歲 | 來自嘉義</p>

        </div>



        <div class="info-section">

            <div class="info-item">

                <span class="info-label">就讀學校</span>

                <span>國立金門大學</span>

            </div>

            <div class="info-item">

                <span class="info-label">就讀科系</span>

                <span>資訊工程學系 (CSIE)</span>

            </div>

            

            <div class="goal-box">

                <strong>未來目標：</strong><br>

                未來希望能在資工領域發展，也希望能不斷提升自己。

            </div>

        </div>



        <footer>

            © 2024 Created by 許毓庭

        </footer>

    </div>



</body>

</html>
